translated: Karlbrink, Doris, dentist, Gothenburg, born 13/2/03 in Umeå to parents: Chief physician Helge Rödén and Doris Malmros. Married on 3/15 to lawyer Gillis Karlbrink. Children: None. Completed studies: High school in Sundsvall '22, dental student '24, dentist '26. Worked in Lindesberg '26-'28, employed by the Stockholm dental association '28-'36, has been practicing in Gothenburg since '35.
